{"tid":2252253,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"國泰大裁員｜空姐590萬低市價賣走映灣園 東涌租務本月急跌近40%","createTime":"2020-10-21T10:52:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-25T04:55:18.000Z","uid":271829,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"063162e8526565d27e9ca34b226ec619c616d0e1","tid":2252253,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T10:52:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/wRYqNr0mAlA1lP49fvVNi_qOG0c=/720x405/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/RKSCNX4NFVAZ3EV32MRVMFZ6AU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FwRYqNr0mAlA1lP49fvVNi_qOG0c%3D%2F720x405%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FRKSCNX4NFVAZ3EV32MRVMFZ6AU.jpg&h=6d76d5a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n單位望山景<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/N4WEdEv1V7j0YbCy_T1abqX7v9M=/720x405/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/GIT2OYAFWJHFBHYX3S5SYPWBWY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FN4WEdEv1V7j0YbCy_T1abqX7v9M%3D%2F720x405%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FGIT2OYAFWJHFBHYX3S5SYPWBWY.jpg&h=42f096ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n映灣園鄰近機場，乃眾多機組人員居住屋苑<br />\n<br />\n...<br />\n疫情重挫全球航空業，本地航空業龍頭，紮根香港逾70年的國泰航空，今早宣佈企業重組，削減約8,500個職位，眾多機組人員居住的東涌區至青衣區一帶，近期已有「無工開」空姐等機組人員劈價賣樓。<br />\n消息指，一名空姐上月以590萬元低價賣走持有多年的映灣園兩房單位。一名國泰機師更可能要蝕讓掟貨，持貨一年恐蝕逾150萬元，成為國泰員工賣樓第一滴血。<br />\n該區地產代理透露，映灣園1座一伙實用面積470方呎低層戶，屬兩房間隔，上月以590萬元，呎價12,553元，比市價略低。據知，單位業主為國泰一名將近退休的菲律賓籍空姐，上月從菲律賓回港接受強制檢疫隔離14天賣樓，單位亦花費逾10萬元翻新。該代理估計，該空姐「應該係聞到味，知道無得留低」，最後樓都要賣，當是提早退休。查冊顯示，上址於2012年以310萬元買入，持貨8年賬面獲利280萬元。<br />\n...<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20201021/W26E4EFG25FQREBQ5B7YIAUDYE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20201021%2FW26E4EFG25FQREBQ5B7YIAUDYE%2F&d=z3Qy88JfdbGSADH60DObPdqeVONt7zbw7GHn8%2FjWPdo%3D&h=ffa15dd7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20201021%2FW26E4EFG25FQREBQ5B7YIAUDYE%2F&h=7fc24289\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20201021/W26E4EFG25FQREBQ5B7YIAUDYE/</a>"},{"pid":"1ff7d805d5ca49d8b5c2e2ccb0dd19c74272a223","tid":2252253,"uid":72757,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T11:21:17.000Z","msg":"1座低層都萬2萬3真係有平到咩"},{"pid":"f0a60f1e3256ee457182497724b9cf00273e9533","tid":2252253,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T11:21:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"344b21a2418026135cd6b98ed9cac5cf0813e47f","tid":2252253,"uid":8328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"063162e8526565d27e9ca34b226ec619c616d0e1","tid":2252253,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T10:52:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/wRYqNr0mAlA1lP49fvVNi_qOG0c=/720x405/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/RKSCNX4NFVAZ3EV32MRVMFZ6AU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FwRYqNr0mAlA1lP49fvVNi_qOG0c%3D%2F720x405%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FRKSCNX4NFVAZ3EV32MRVMFZ6AU.jpg&h=6d76d5a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n單位望山景<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/N4WEdEv1V7j0YbCy_T1abqX7v9M=/720x405/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/GIT2OYAFWJHFBHYX3S5SYPWBWY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%